        <h2>Key features for HVAC businesses</h2>

        <h3>For HVAC service companies</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Maintenance agreement / service contract management</li>
          <li>Equipment history per customer location (unit model, install date, warranty)</li>
          <li>Dispatch board with real-time technician GPS</li>
          <li>Flat-rate pricing presentation on mobile</li>
          <li>Customer communication: arrival windows, technician photos, review requests</li>
          <li>Financing integration for system replacements</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>For commercial HVAC subs</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>AIA G702/G703 billing generation</li>
          <li>Job cost tracking vs. bid by cost code</li>
          <li>Change order management with GC approval</li>
          <li>Subcontractor compliance (duct fab subs, insulation, etc.)</li>
          <li>Scheduling coordination with equipment delivery</li>
          <li>QuickBooks integration for payroll and accounting</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Decision guide by business type</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Small HVAC service company:</strong> Jobber</li>
          <li><strong>Growing HVAC service company (5+ techs):</strong> ServiceTitan</li>
